parameters:
Would you like to view the event? Once more! The Fake Virgin
Auction

\nc<Senpai>Everyone is doing well. At this rate, it seems we won't have
any problems achieving our team's quarterly goals.
\nc<Saki>Does each team have a quota to meet?

\nc<Member 1>Of course. By the way, if a team can't meet its quota... in
the worst case, we could all be sent to work at the factory
as a group.

\nc<Senpai>There's no need to worry. If you meet your individual quota,
the team's quota will naturally be fulfilled as well.
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Phew, that's a surprisingly normal system for our company.

\nc<Member 1>Our team tends to meet the quota early thanks to Meary-
senpai.
\nc<Senpai>Don't relax just yet. That's only for the energy quota.

\nc<Senpai>Yes. In addition to energy, there's also a revenue quota for
the team. Simply put, we need to achieve a target sales
figure.

\nc<Senpai>Exactly. This term, the revenue quota is looking a bit
risky.

\nc<Member 2>Why is that? With Saki joining, our revenue should have
increased.

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Because we haven't been doing enough work that brings in
money. Maybe everyone's been focusing too much on
promotional activities?
\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>To achieve our target, we need at least one big hit.

\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Senpai>Does anyone have a source of money? Like a regular customer
who's a big spender.

\nc<Member 3>It's almost the end of the half-year period, we don't have
anything like that left...

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Think a little more creatively. Saki, don't just stay
silent, give us your opinion too.
\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Yes. I want to hear the opinion of a newcomer too.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Suddenly asking me that... um, what kind of activities
usually generate the most revenue?

\nc<Member 1>Well, mostly we earn by entertaining clients at the company.
And...

\nc<Senpai>The price of a succubus is highest when she loses her
virginity. I told you about this before, didn't I?

\nc<Saki>(Ah... right. Indeed, they said the revenue from that time
was amazing) But there are no more virgins in our team,
right?

\nc<Senpai>Yes, you were the last one. Besides, most succubi lose their
virginity at an early stage anyway.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>So, this method isn't an option then...

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>It's too early to give up. If we don't have a virgin, we'll
just have to create one, right?

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Whaaat?! Sell my virginity again? How is that even
possible??

\nc<Senpai>Think about it. The last virgin auction was a secret event
only for VIPs. The general customers don't even know such an
event took place.
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>But I've been working continuously since then!

\nc<Senpai>That's why we'll quietly proceed with customers who don't
know much about Saki. If it succeeds, we'll reach our target
in no time!
\nc<Member 3>That's a good idea! We don't have any other alternatives...

\nc<Member 2>We'll handle the preparations, so Saki, you just need to
sell your virginity.

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>That's fraud, isn't it?! Why is everyone so serious about
selling a fictional virginity!

\nc<Saki>Of course I dislike it! I'm the one who has to act in front
of the customers! And I have to perform that crazy
performance again, right?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>We have no choice! Let's all get sent to work at the factory
together~

\nc<Senpai>You can't just live doing only what you like. When I was
young, I wanted to become a demon lord, you know?

\nc<Saki>...Is that like being the president of the demon world or
something?

\nc<Senpai>Well, something like that. We need to start contacting
people quickly! Let's just reuse the materials as they are.
\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>In the end, I don't have the right to refuse, do I...
